{"tid":1068201,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港新加坡巴黎並列全球生活開支最貴城市","createTime":"2019-03-19T05:15:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-19T14:21:20.000Z","uid":75969,"like":23,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"4178448b06ec880dd48c883a288f65c01dce2420","tid":1068201,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T05:15:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190319/s00001/c9b0822207a7968f4328720cdc970f32.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190319%2Fs00001%2Fc9b0822207a7968f4328720cdc970f32.jpg&h=458ef6d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n英國經濟學人智庫（Economist Intelligence Unit）公布年度生活開支最昂貴城市排行榜。在133個上榜城市中，香港較上一次調查上升3位，與新加坡及法國巴黎並列第一，是有關調查進行30多年來，第一次出現三城並立首位的情況。<br />\n<br />\n負責研究的學者斯拉夫查娃（Roxana Slavcheva）表示，結果反映在全球化影響以及消費模式日漸相似下，各地大城市的生活開支變得愈來愈貴。她又稱，即使一些城市生活開支較低，未來也會因各項交通及公共服務等費用上升，而推高整體生活費。<br />\n<br />\n其餘頭十城市，依次為第四位的瑞士蘇黎世、並列第五位的瑞士日內瓦和日本大阪、並列第七位的韓國首爾、丹麥哥本哈根和美國紐約，以及並列第十位的以色列特拉維夫和美國洛杉磯。<br />\n<br />\n（英國廣播公司/路透社）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190319/s00001/1552966632246/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190319%2Fs00001%2F1552966632246%2F&d=pHv7ulxaPAPTUdGhwq1YMQbFtlMfP7wF5OAPhGI7yCY%3D&h=4c1138cf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190319%2Fs00001%2F1552966632246%2F&h=0b7ca940\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190319/s00001/1552966632246/</a>"},{"pid":"4854210b1f4c8da65696020262431f1d71b4722a","tid":1068201,"uid":61280,"like":37,"dislike":1,"score":36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T05:19:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">熱烈祝賀香港：<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src